 LONDON, July 6, 2017 – Bain Capital Credit and HSBC announced today that they have partnered to refinance the existing debt of Adler & Allan with a unitranche loan. Adler & Allan is one of the UK’s leading providers of specialist environmental and related asset resilience services and... 






