Company Overview of Bain Capital Fund IX, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bain Capital Fund IX, L.P. specializes in private equity investments through buyouts. It prefers to invest in companies engaged in the energy, healthcare, materials, industrials, consumer discretionary, consumer goods, information technology, utilities, financials, and telecommunication sectors. The fund focuses on investing globally with a focus on America.


